-- Steel Authority of India, JSW Cut Prices of Flat Products by as Much as 2%
-- B y   A b h i s h e k   S h a n k e r
-- 2010-11-01T15:11:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/steel-authority-of-india-jsw-cut-prices-of-flat-products-by-as-much-as-2-.html
Steel Authority of India Ltd. cut
prices of flat products, used to make cars, by as much as 2
percent for November, spokesman R.K. Singhal said in a phone
interview today.  Rival JSW Steel Ltd. also cut prices by the same amount,
Marketing Director Jayant Acharya said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
